Usage: analyze_joule_heat [-help] [-detail_delta_temperature_file <string>]
                          [-detail_delta_temperature_region <string>]
                          [-domain <string>] [-net <string>]
                          [-output_directory <string>]
                          [-report_conn_pin_wire <string>]
                          [-scale_rms_limit <float>]
                          [-tile_delta_temperature_file <string>]
                          [-tiles <string>]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-detail_delta_temperature_file <string>  # detailed delta temperature file
                                         # (string, optional)
-detail_delta_temperature_region <string>
                                         # detailed delta temperature region (string, optional)
-domain <string>                         # domain name (string, optional)
-net <string>                            # net name (string, optional)
-output_directory <string>               # joule-heat output dir
                                         # (string, optional)
-report_conn_pin_wire <string>           # report results on wires connecting
                                         # to cell pins (string, optional)
-scale_rms_limit <float>                 # RMS EM limit scale factor
                                         # (float, optional)
-tile_delta_temperature_file <string>    # tile delta temperature file
                                         # (string, optional)
-tiles <string>                          # number of map tiles <num_x num_y>
                                         # (string, optional)